A simple Pong written in LÖVE Lua. 

The final Version (1.0.0 and above) will be having the following features:

- Main Menu with customizable Options like:
	- Modified Ball Color
	- Modified Avatars
	- Modified Speed for the Characters
	- Modified Speed for the Ball
	- Modified Background Music
	- Volume
	- Changable Rules
	- Changable Window Size
	- Debugging Mode
- A fully working version of Pong
- Real Physics thanks to the LÖVE engine